{"tid":2082980,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"X偏方 全民拆解[粵]     ","createTime":"2020-06-28T12:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T13:41:43.000Z","uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"04e64514daec184009d04b710b4b86148727e996","tid":2082980,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:36:06.000Z","msg":"X偏方 全民拆解[粵]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n試用偏方之前，記得要「FC」！「媽媽網」指蒜頭冰糖水是止咳偏方，杜穎珊、呂靜文找來專家測試白蒜、獨子蒜、黑蒜的功效。冰糖有助止咳化痰，更是古代喉糖。陸浩明聲稱食花椒或飲焗花椒水，均可舒緩過敏性哮喘，中醫、西醫各有甚麼見解？紅茶、綠茶等茶類會經過不同的發酵程度；而喝茶或用綠茶漱口，也能夠對抗流感病毒？「街頭偏方」環節，余德丞品嚐三間店舖的滋補潤肺燉湯。貴價款式主打足料湯頭，而燉湯冷飲更有「追喝性」！"},{"pid":"6e5a09ad670e2d77b840bd76aea6996c40518d25","tid":2082980,"uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"有sandy"},{"pid":"86f7398561fbb10c6961b100213696eab0491721","tid":2082980,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾後生女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e32bbc39c52186ad0d0b45d62abb4a84e3b9d66","tid":2082980,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"條女好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊個黎?"},{"pid":"84bd9b99d63b005f75ede0993f124d7c19c3b9ee","tid":2082980,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86f7398561fbb10c6961b100213696eab0491721","tid":2082980,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾後生女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.g